data.description: Don't miss out on this lovingly maintained and updated 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home in New Ulm! As soon as you enter you will notice the timeless quality combined with wonderful updates which include new carpet on the open staircase and upper level, new upper level bathroom, freshly painted walls throughout, and beautiful new vinyl plank flooring on the main floor. The living room is spacious and bright which opens up into a great dining space. The refreshed kitchen offers ample cabinetry and prep space. Adjoining the kitchen is a convenient powder room and access to the unfinished basement. All three bedrooms and a full bathroom are located upstairs. Completing this home is a spacious corner lot, concrete patio, and an awesome 24 x 38 heated detached garage! You are going to love it - schedule a showing today!
